										link="#"

				/>
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="Blog" class="w-full h-full mb-10">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-primary underline">
				Blog Posts
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg mt-2">
				If a topic catches my interest, I will write a blog post about it.
				These posts are usually technical in nature, but I may also write
				about other topics that I find interesting.
			</p>
			<div class="w-full h-fit grid grid-cols-1 gap-4">
				{allPosts.map((post: any) =>
				<Card
					title={post.frontmatter.title}
					description={post.frontmatter.description}
					link={'/Æ’/'+post.frontmatter.title}
				/>
				)}
			</div>
		</section>
		<section id="videos" class="w-full h-full mb-10">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-black text-primary underline">
				Videos
			</h1>
			<p class="text-lg mt-2">
				If a Project or a topic is interesting enough, I will make a video
				about it. These videos are usually technical in nature, but I may
				also make videos about other topics that I find interesting.
